(nICacheTLBWays, power_internal).explanation: Increasing instruction cache TLB associativity requires additional comparators and selection logic, which directly increases internal power consumption of the TLB structure;

(nICacheTLBWays, area_net_area).explanation: Higher TLB associativity necessitates more interconnect wiring between additional comparison units and selection logic, directly increasing the net area for routing;

(nICacheTLBWays, nDCacheTLBWays).explanation: The associativity of instruction cache TLB and data cache TLB are independent microarchitectural design parameters that do not causally influence each other;
